    <description>
The NirExt utility add 3 useful context menu extensions to your Windows Explorer environment:

* <span class="special2">Folder Properties: </span>
This option is available in the context menu when you right-click on a folder in your file system.
It allows you change the icon of any folder you want, and change the text that appears when the mouse cursor moves over the folder.
